<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Phylogram of Cytospora from a Maximum Likelihood analysis, based on ITS sequences. MP, ML and BI bootstrap support values are shown in order. The tree is rooted with Diaporthe vaccinii. Strains in the current study are in blue." , "Figure 4. Morphology of Cytospora rhizophorae from Sonneratia apetala. A-B. Conidiomata; C-D. Transverse sections through conidiomata; E-F. Conidiophores; G-H. Conidia. Scale bars: A-B = 200 μm; C = 100 μm; D = 50 μm; E-G = 10 μm; H = 5 μm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/450201" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/417598" .

